cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

The paper deals with image classification and retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning models and optimization techniques also suggests the machine learning (cs.MM) and learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the challenges of cross-domain retrieval, which involves dealing with large variations in image characteristics, indicating the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Lastly, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for generating category labels, which suggests the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
